ness Value, then to Criticality.",\n    "cia_rating_scale": "4-level: Insignificant, Moderate, Serious, Extreme",\n    "cia_definitions_source": "Asset Management Guidelines_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx, Table 3; Risk Assessment Template_For Agentic AI RM Use Case.xlsx, Sheet: Asset Inventorization Guideline",\n    "business_value_calculation_method": "Asset Value Chart/Matrix (lookup table based on CIA combinations)",\n    "business_value_levels": [\n      "Very Low",\n      "Low",\n      "Medium",\n      "High",\n      "Very High"\n    ],\n    "business_value_source": "Risk Assessment Template_For Agentic AI RM Use Case.xlsx, Sheet: Asset Inventory (lookup logic)",\n    "criticality_classification_method": "Business Value to Criticality Mapping Table",\n    "criticality_levels": [\n      "Insignificant",\n      "Low Critical",\n      "Medium Critical",\n      "High Critical",\n      "Very High Critical"\n    ],\n    "criticality_source": "Asset Management Guidelines_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx, Table 4; Asset Management SOP, Table 3",\n    "searches_performed": [\n      "What impact assessment methodology is used? CIA? DREAD? Custom?",\n      "What rating scale is used for CIA impact ratings? What are the levels?",\n      "How is Asset Business Value calculated or determined from CIA impact ratings? Is there a matrix, chart, or formula?",\n      "How is Asset Criticality Classification determined from Asset Business Value?",\n      "Mapping from Insignificant, Moderate, Serious, Extreme to numeric values 1-5 for CIA impact ratings or overall impact calculation"\n    ]\n  },\n  "threat_analysis": [\n    {\n      "threat_id": "threat_1",\n      "threat_name": "Security threats to Employee Laptop",\n      "threat_description": "Comprehensive risk assessment for New Employee Laptop based on 20 detailed questionnaire responses covering security posture, controls, and compliance",\n      "impact_assessment": {\n        "confidentiality": {\n          "rating": "Serious",\n          "numeric_value": 3,\n          "reasoning": "Based on questionnaire answer ''[3. Data & Application Facts] Q: What types of sensitive or critical data are stored or processed on this Employee Laptop? Answer: [''financial_corporate'']'' and ''[3. Data & Application Facts] Q: Approximately how much sensitive data (if any) is stored locally on this laptop? Answer: medium'', unauthorized disclosure of ''financial_corporate'' data, even a medium amount, would cause significant harm to the organization''s interests. This meets the discovered definition for ''Serious'' for Loss of Confidentiality: ''Unauthorized disclosure within or outside the organization would cause significant harm to the interest of the organization.'' While full disk encryption and MFA are present, the presence of sensitive financial data locally elevates the impact."\n        },\n        "integrity": {\n          "rating": "Serious",\n          "numeric_value": 3,\n          "reasoning": "Based on questionnaire answer ''[2. Business Context and Usage] Q: What is the primary business purpose or function of this Employee Laptop? Answer: Daily operations - Finance analysis'', ''[3. Data & Application Facts] Q: What types of sensitive or critical data are stored or processed on this Employee Laptop? Answer: [''financial_corporate'']'', and ''[3. Data & Application Facts] Q: Does this laptop run any business-critical applications that are not easily replaceable or have unique configurations? Answer: yes'', the laptop handles critical financial data and applications. The fact that ''[4. Security Control Facts] Q: Are operating system and application security patches applied regularly (e.g., monthly, automatically) to this Employee Laptop? Answer: no'' indicates a significant vulnerability. Unauthorized modification or damage to financial analysis data or business-critical applications, exacerbated by patching gaps, is expected to have a serious adverse effect on business operations. This meets the discovered definition for ''Serious'' for Loss of Integrity: ''Unauthorized modification or damage of information is expected to have a serious adverse effect on business operations.''"\n        },\n        "availability": {\n          "rating": "Serious",\n          "numeric_value": 3,\n          "reasoning": "Based on questionnaire answer ''[2. Business Context and Usage] Q: What is the primary business purpose or function of this Employee Laptop? Answer: Daily operations - Finance analysis'' and ''[3. Data & Application Facts] Q: Does this laptop run any business-critical applications that are not easily replaceable or have unique configurations? Answer: yes'', the laptop is critical for daily finance operations and runs business-critical applications. Although ''[4. Security Control Facts] Q: Is a corporate backup solution (e.g., cloud backup, network drive sync) actively used for data on this Employee Laptop? Answer: yes_automatic'' provides some mitigation, the lack of regular OS and application patching (''[4. Security Control Facts] Q: Are operating system and application security patches applied regularly (e.g., monthly, automatically) to this Employee Laptop? Answer: no'') increases the risk of prolonged unavailability. Disruption of access to these critical functions and data would have a serious adverse effect on business operations. This meets the discovered definition for ''Serious'' for Loss of Availability: ''Impact of disruption of access or unavailability of information or information asset or services is expected to have a serious adverse effect on business operations.''"\n        }\n      },\n      "overall_impact_calculation": {\n        "confidentiality_numeric": 3,\n        "integrity_numeric": 3,\n        "availability_numeric": 3,\n        "calculation_method": "Derived from Asset Business Value mapping to Impact Category",\n        "calculation": "Asset Business Value ''High'' maps to Impact Rating ''4''",\n        "overall_impact": "High",\n        "overall_impact_numeric": 4\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  "asset_business_value": {\n    "cia_combination": "Serious, Serious, Serious",\n    "cia_combination_key": "Serious|Serious|Serious",\n    "business_value_rating": "High",\n    "calculation_method": "Asset Value Chart (discovered from Risk Assessment Template_For Agentic AI RM Use Case.xlsx, Sheet: Asset Inventory)",\n    "calculation_details": "Per discovered Asset Value Chart: CIA combination (Serious, Serious, Serious) maps to Business Value ''High''",\n    "source_reference": "Risk Assessment Template_For Agentic AI RM Use Case.xlsx, Sheet: Asset Inventory",\n    "reasoning": "Based on calculated CIA ratings (Confidentiality: Serious, Integrity: Serious, Availability: Serious), per the discovered Asset Value Chart in the organizational Risk Assessment Template, the Asset Business Value is ''High''."\n  },\n  "asset_criticality": {\n    "criticality_classification": "High Critical",\n    "business_value_input": "High",\n    "calculation_method": "Criticality Classification Table (discovered from Asset Management Guidelines_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx, Table 4)",\n    "calculation_details": "Per discovered Criticality Classification Table: Business Value ''High'' maps to Criticality ''High Critical''",\n    "source_reference": "Asset Management Guidelines_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx, Table 4",\n    "reasoning": "Based on calculated Asset Business Value ''High'', per the discovered Criticality Classification Table in the organizational Asset Management Guidelines, the Asset Criticality Classification is ''High Critical''."\n  }\n}','\n',char(10)),replace('{\n  "discovery_summary": {\n    "methodology": "Quantitative",\n    "risk_calculation": {\n      "method": "Formula",\n      "formula": "Risk Impact Rating \u00d7 Risk Probability Rating",\n      "description": "Risk Value (RV) is computed by multiplying the Risk Impact Rating (RI) by the Risk Probability Rating (RP). The resulting RV is then mapped to a Risk Evaluation Rating."\n    },\n    "probability_scale": {\n      "type": "Numeric",\n      "levels": [\n        "Very Low",\n        "Low",\n        "Medium",\n        "High",\n        "Very High"\n      ],\n      "range": "1-5"\n    },\n    "impact_scale": {\n      "type": "Numeric",\n      "levels": [\n        "Very Low",\n        "Low",\n        "Medium",\n        "High",\n        "Very High"\n      ],\n      "range": "1-5"\n    },\n    "risk_level_mapping": {\n      "method": "Value range mapping",\n      "levels": [\n        "Rating 1",\n        "Rating 2",\n        "Rating 3",\n        "Rating 4",\n        "Rating 5"\n      ],\n      "thresholds": "Risk Value 0-5 maps to Rating 1; 6-10 maps to Rating 2; 11-15 maps to Rating 3; 16-20 maps to Rating 4; 21-25 maps to Rating 5"\n    },\n    "acceptance_criteria": "Risk Ratings 1-2 are Acceptable Risk; Risk Ratings 3-5 are Non Acceptable Risk",\n    "questionnaire_answers_used": true\n  },\n  "summary": {\n    "total_threats_assessed": 1,\n    "highest_risk_value": 12,\n    "non_acceptable_risks_count": 1,\n    "acceptable_risks_count": 0,\n    "overall_risk_level": "Rating 3"\n  },\n  "threat_risk_quantification": [\n    {\n      "threat": "Security threats to Employee Laptop",\n      "vulnerabilities": [\n        "Security gaps identified through questionnaire assessment"\n      ],\n      "risk_statement": "Comprehensive risk assessment for New Employee Laptop based on 20 detailed questionnaire responses covering security posture, controls, and compliance",\n      "risk_impact": {\n        "rating": 4,\n        "category": "High",\n        "reasoning": "Based on Agent 1 CIA assessment: Confidentiality=Serious (3), Integrity=Serious (3), Availability=Serious (3). Overall impact derived from Asset Business Value ''High'' mapping to Impact Rating ''4''."\n      },\n      "risk_probability": {\n        "rating": 3,\n        "category": "Medium",\n        "reasoning": "Based on questionnaire answer ''[4. Security Control Facts] Q: Are operating system and application security patches applied regularly (e.g., monthly, automatically) to this Employee Laptop? Answer: no'', indicating a critical vulnerability that significantly increases the probability of exploitation. Also, ''[2. Business Context and Usage] Q: Is this Employee Laptop regularly used outside of corporate premises (e.g., home, travel)? Answer: yes_occasionally'' increases exposure. The asset owner''s own assessment in ''[5. Overall Risk Perspective] Q: Considering all identified threats and vulnerabilities, what is the estimated ''Probability Rating'' of a severe compromise occurring to this Employee Laptop within the next year? Answer: 3'' aligns with a ''Medium'' probability (once every 4-6 months)."\n      },\n      "risk_value": {\n        "value": 12,\n        "calculation": "4 (impact) \u00d7 3 (probability) = 12"\n      },\n      "risk_evaluation_rating": {\n        "rating": 3,\n        "level": "Rating 3",\n        "mapping_rationale": "Risk value 12 maps to Risk Rating 3 per discovered risk evaluation table (11 to 15)."\n      },\n      "risk_classification": {\n        "classification": "NON-ACCEPTABLE",\n        "criteria_applied": "Risk Ratings 3 to 5 are classified as Non Acceptable Risk.",\n        "justification": "Risk Evaluation Rating 3 falls within the Non Acceptable Risk category per organizational policy."\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  "rag_queries_performed": [\n    "risk quantification methodology"\n  ],\n  "rag_sources_consulted": [\n    "Risk Management Guidelines_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx",\n    "Risk Management SOP_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx",\n    "ISO IEC 27005-2022.pdf"\n  ]\n}','\n',char(10)),replace('{\n  "discovery_summary": {\n    "control_framework": "ISO 27001, ITGC",\n    "control_categories": [\n      "Organizational",\n      "People",\n      "Physical",\n      "Technological",\n      "Access to Programs and Data",\