when the laptop is used for occasional remote access to corporate resources.",\n      "impact_assessment": {\n        "confidentiality": {\n          "rating": "Extreme",\n          "numeric_value": 5,\n          "reasoning": "Based on questionnaire answer [3. Data Stored & Processed] stating ''Restricted'' data classification, and sensitive data types [''PHI'', ''PII'', ''PCI_DSS'', ''Financial_Proprietary''] with ''Medium'' volume, unauthorized disclosure via compromised credentials would cause ''serious damage to the interests of the organization''. This meets the discovered definition for ''Extreme'' Confidentiality from Asset Management Guidelines_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx (Table 3)."\n        },\n        "integrity": {\n          "rating": "Extreme",\n          "numeric_value": 5,\n          "reasoning": "Based on questionnaire answer [2. Business Context & Usage] listing critical functions and the presence of ''Restricted'' data including [''PHI'', ''PII'', ''PCI_DSS'', ''Financial_Proprietary''], an attacker with compromised credentials and local admin privileges could cause ''severe and long ranging adverse effect on business operations'' through unauthorized modification or damage. This meets the discovered definition for ''Extreme'' Integrity from Asset Management Guidelines_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx (Table 3)."\n        },\n        "availability": {\n          "rating": "Extreme",\n          "numeric_value": 5,\n          "reasoning": "Based on questionnaire answer [2. Business Context & Usage] listing critical functions like ''Sales order processing'', ''Software development'', ''Financial reporting'', and ''Customer support'', an attacker with compromised credentials could render the system unavailable, leading to ''severe and long ranging adverse effect on business operations''. This meets the discovered definition for ''Extreme'' Availability from Asset Management Guidelines_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx (Table 3)."\n    