ulatory penalties, and severe reputational damage.",\n      "risk_impact": {\n        "rating": 4,\n        "category": "Extreme",\n        "reasoning": "Based on Agent 1 CIA assessment: Confidentiality=Extreme (4), Integrity=Extreme (4), Availability=Serious (3). Overall impact is max(4,4,3) = 4 (Extreme)."\n      },\n      "risk_probability": {\n        "rating": 4,\n        "category": "High",\n        "reasoning": "The lack of SIEM integration (Q15: No) significantly increases the probability of undetected compromise. Informal false positive management (Q18: Informally managed) can lead to alert fatigue. While 24/7 monitoring (Q17: Yes) is a control, its effectiveness is reduced by these factors. This makes a compromise leading to undetected exfiltration likely to occur once every 1-3 months."\n      },\n      "risk_value": {\n        "value": 16,\n        "calculation": "4 (impact) \u00d7 4 (probability) = 16"\n      },\n      "risk_evaluation_rating": {\n        "rating": 4,\n        "level": "High",\n        "mapping_rationale": "Risk value 16 maps to Rating 4 (High) per discovered risk level mapping (16-20)."\n      },\n      "risk_classification": {\n        "classification": "NON-ACCEPTABLE",\n        "criteria_applied": "Risk Evaluation Rating 3-5 is Non-Acceptable.",\n        "justification": "Risk Evaluation Rating 4 (High) is non-acceptable per organizational policy."\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  "rag_queries_performed": [\n    "risk quantification methodology"\n  ],\n  "rag_sources_consulted": [\n    "Risk Management Guidelines_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx",\n    "Risk Management SOP_For RM Agentic AI Use Case v1.0.docx"\n  ]\n}','\n',char(10)),replace('{\n  "discovery_summary": {\n    "control_framework": "ISO 27001, ITGC, NIST RMF",\n    "control_categories": [\n      "Preventive",\n      "Detective",\n      "Corrective"\n    ],\n    "control_types": [\n      "Preventive",\n      "Detective",\n      "Corrective"\n    ],\n    "effectiveness_scale