 security incidents."}, "Q_ASSET_INVENTORY_PHYSICAL": {"question_text": "Is there a current and accurate inventory of critical physical assets (e.g., servers, specialized equipment, sensitive documents) housed within this building?", "answer": "Yes", "question_type": "dropdown", "section": "4. Emergency Preparedness and Operational Controls", "help_text": "Refers to an inventory of physical items, not just the building itself.\n\n\ud83d\udca1 Why this matters: Fact about an administrative control that helps in asset tracking, recovery, and impact assessment during an incident.", "why_this_matters": "Fact about an administrative control that helps in asset tracking, recovery, and impact assessment during an incident."}, "Q_OVERALL_IMPACT_RATING": {"question_text": "Considering all identified risks and existing controls, what is the estimated overall ''Impact Rating'' if this Office Building were to be severely compromised (e.g., prolonged unavailability, major physical damage, significant security breach)?", "answer": "4 - High: Risk has serious impact on business and operations", "question_type": "dropdown", "section": "5. Overall Risk Perspective", "help_text": "Rate the overall business impact using the organization''s scale (1-5). This is your overall business judgment, not a technical calculation.\n\n\ud83d\udca1 Why this matters: Collects the asset owner''s high-level business perspective on potential harm, which is a critical input for Agent 2''s risk quantification.", "why_this_matters": "Collects the asset owner''s high-level business perspective on potential harm, which is a critical input for Agent 2''s risk quantification."}, "Q_OVERALL_PROBABILITY_RATING": {"question_text": "Considering all identified threats and vulnerabilities, what is the estimated ''Probability Rating'' of a severe compromise occurring to this Office Building within the next year?", "answer": "4 - High: Once every 1-3 months", "question_type": "dropdown", "section": "5. Overall Risk 