 loss of protection'' means that the integrity of the protected systems could be compromised. While not a direct malicious modification, the failure could lead to an environment where unauthorized modifications are more likely or where system integrity is degraded. This is expected to have a ''moderate adverse effect on business operations''. This meets the discovered definition for ''Moderate'': ''Unauthorized modification or damage of information is expected to have a moderate adverse effect on business operations''."}, "availability": {"rating": "Serious", "numeric_value": 3, "reasoning": "The threat explicitly states ''operational disruption to Manufacturing Line Control'' and ''system instability'' due to the software failure. The unavailability of the endpoint protection or the instability of the protected systems would have a ''serious adverse effect on business operations''. This meets the discovered definition for ''Serious'': ''Impact of disruption of access or unavailability of information or information asset or services is expected to have a serious adverse effect on business operations''."}}, "overall_impact_calculation": {"confidentiality_numeric": 1, "integrity_numeric": 2, "availability_numeric": 3, "calculation_method": "max(C, I, A)", "calculation": "max(1, 2, 3) = 3", "overall_impact": "3 - Serious", "overall_impact_numeric": 3}}], "asset_cia_ratings": {"confidentiality": {"rating": "Extreme", "numeric_value": 4, "reasoning": "Asset-level CIA: Maximum C value across all threats. Threat 1: Moderate(2), Threat 2: Extreme(4), Threat 3: Insignificant(1)  Asset C = Extreme(4)", "threat_breakdown": ["Threat 1: Moderate(2)", "Threat 2: Extreme(4)", "Threat 3: Insignificant(1)"]}, "integrity": {"rating": "Extreme", "numeric_value": 4, "reasoning": "Asset-level CIA: Maximum I value across all threats. Threat 1: Serious(3), Threat 2: Extreme(4), Threat 3: Moderate(2)  Asset I = Extreme(4)", "threat_breakdown": ["Threat 1: Serious(3)", "Threat 2: Extreme(4)