ization may harm the interest of the organization''."}, "integrity": {"rating": "Serious", "numeric_value": 3, "reasoning": "The threat of ''widespread malware infection'' directly impacts the accuracy and completeness of data and systems. Given that the asset protects ''Manufacturing Line Control'', unauthorized modification or damage of information is expected to have a ''serious adverse effect on business operations''. This meets the discovered definition for ''Serious'': ''Unauthorized modification or damage of information is expected to have a serious adverse effect on business operations''."}, "availability": {"rating": "Extreme", "numeric_value": 4, "reasoning": "The contextual description and risk statement clearly indicate ''disruption to Manufacturing Line Control'' and ''operational downtime'' due to widespread malware. The unavailability of critical manufacturing systems would have a ''severe and long ranging adverse effect on business operations''. This meets the discovered definition for ''Extreme'': ''Impact of disruption of access or unavailability of information or information asset or services is expected to have severe and long ranging adverse effect on business operations''."}}, "overall_impact_calculation": {"confidentiality_numeric": 2, "integrity_numeric": 3, "availability_numeric": 4, "calculation_method": "max(C, I, A)", "calculation": "max(2, 3, 4) = 4", "overall_impact": "4 - Extreme", "overall_impact_numeric": 4}}, {"threat_id": "threat_2", "threat_name": "Bypass of Endpoint Protection via Exploitation of Significant Exclusions", "threat_description": "The ''Company-wide Endpoint Protection Platform'' has ''significant exclusions'' configured in its policies, which protect 50 endpoints vital for ''Manufacturing Line Control''. While automatic updates and advanced features like DLP are in place, these exclusions represent a critical blind spot. A sophisticated attacker could leverage knowledge of these exclusions (e.g., specific files, fol