he ''Full Disk Encryption missing'' gap to protect data at rest on the laptop from unauthorized access in case of loss or theft.", "effectiveness_rating": "4/5 (High)", "estimated_cost": "$50 - $150 per device (software license/implementation)", "implementation_timeline": "2-4 weeks (deployment & configuration)", "expected_risk_reduction": "High (significantly reduces data compromise risk from physical loss)", "priority_level": "HIGH"}, {"control_id": "A.8.5", "control_name": "Implement Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)", "why_needed": "Addresses the ''Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) missing'' gap to significantly enhance authentication security and reduce the risk of unauthorized access through compromised credentials.", "effectiveness_rating": "4/5 (High)", "estimated_cost": "$10 - $50 per user/device annually (service subscription)", "implementation_timeline": "4-6 weeks (integration & rollout)", "expected_risk_reduction": "High (drastically reduces unauthorized access probability)", "priority_level": "HIGH"}, {"control_id": "A.8.33", "control_name": "Implement Automated OS and Application Patch Management", "why_needed": "Addresses the ''Regular OS and Application Patching missing'' gap to ensure timely remediation of vulnerabilities and protect against known exploits.", "effectiveness_rating": "4/5 (High)", "estimated_cost": "$20 - $100 per device annually (management solution)", "implementation_timeline": "6-8 weeks (setup & initial patching cycle)", "expected_risk_reduction": "High (reduces vulnerability to known exploits)", "priority_level": "HIGH"}, {"control_id": "A.8.13", "control_name": "Implement Critical User Data Backup", "why_needed": "Addresses the ''Critical User Data Backup missing'' gap to ensure the recoverability of critical user data in the event of data loss due to system failure, malware, or theft.", "effectiveness_rating": "4/5 (High)", "estimated_cost": "$5 - $20 per user/month (cloud storage/backup service)", "implementation_timeline": 